(
<emphasis box="[238,384,1467,1493]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="154">Distichalius</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[404,526,1468,1493]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="154">gissaricus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[537,632,1467,1493]" pageId="13" pageNumber="154" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
above. More material is needed to confirm its identity and, if appropriate, describe the new species.
</paragraph>
